WEBVTT

00:00:00.703 --> 00:00:03.515
This is how war starts.

00:00:03.515 --> 00:00:06.781
One day you're living your ordinary life,

00:00:06.781 --> 00:00:09.297
you're planning to go to a party,

00:00:09.297 --> 00:00:11.681
you're taking your children to school,

00:00:11.681 --> 00:00:14.394
you're making a dentist appointment.

00:00:14.394 --> 00:00:18.020
The next thing, the telephones go out,

00:00:18.020 --> 00:00:21.957
the TVs go out, there's armed men on the street,

00:00:21.957 --> 00:00:24.273
there's roadblocks.

00:00:24.273 --> 00:00:28.750
Your life as you know it goes into suspended animation.

00:00:28.750 --> 00:00:30.955
It stops.